# Deployment

- **Platform:** [Coolify](https://control.bamsignal.com) — self-hosted on the BamSignal server.
- **Production URL:** https://bamsignal.com
- **Do not use Vercel** for this repo (`.vercel/` is legacy/unused).

## How to deploy

1. Commit and push to `main` on `github.com/bamsignalhq/bamsignal`.
2. Coolify rebuilds from the repo `Dockerfile` (`npm run build` → `node server/production.js`).
3. Confirm deploy status in Coolify at control.bamsignal.com (manual redeploy if webhook did not fire).

## Build args / env

See `.env.example` — Coolify injects `VITE_*` at build time and server secrets at runtime (`DATABASE_URL`, `PAYSTACK_SECRET_KEY`, Supabase, etc.).
